list1= []
list2 = []
for i in tqdm(range(0,data.shape[0])):
    for j in range(data2.shape[0]):
        if data.loc[i,'ticker'] == data2.loc[j,'ticker_unique']:
            list1.append(data2.loc[j,'Stock Exchange'])
            list2.append(data2.loc[j,'Sector'])
            break
